verbose_text: As demonstrated in XREF_FIG, overexpression of MMP2 significantly attenuated the protective effects of miR-185-5p in NP cells treated with TNF-alpha and IL-1beta, suggesting that miR-185-5p regulated NP cell function by targeting MMP2.
